title: StarCraft plus exp-no install
description:
A Virusboy Production.

Welcome to Starcraft, where you are the Commander, an unsung Battle Strategist commanding heroes and the likes at your disposal.  Play over 40 Maps in Campaign, or go head to head in free play, or get daring with an on-line Multi player skirmish that can hold a 4 on 4 battle.  Choose Map Editor to create and conquer the other team.

Choose from three seperate and unqiue races; Zerg, Protoss, and the Terrain. Nuke, Zerg, or Obliterate everything in sight.  Download and play right away.  No extraction needed.

Blizzard North INC.  Now Battle.Net.
Like the first one go buy the second one.
